      "startTime": 191.3592405796
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンお疲れ様。星見まつりに向けて\n練習にも熱が入っているようだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job with the lesson.\nYou seem really motivated for the Hoshimi Festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.4333426793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、ライブの後にサニピのみんなで浴衣を着て\nお祭りを見て回る約束をしたんだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I heard you and the Sunny Peace members planned to\nwear yukatas and explore the festival after the live show?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.3375627838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "そのつもりだったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was the plan‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.2445990801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "予定が変わっちゃって\n私だけライブの後はみんなと別行動なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The schedule changed.\nI'll be going my separate way after the live show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.6779324134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "星見まつりをあんなに楽しみにしていたのに\n千紗は見て行かないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were looking forward to the Hoshimi Festival so much.\nAren't you going to check it out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.3333426793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、お祭りは見て回ります\nただ、一緒に行く相手はみんなじゃなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I will go to the festival.\nIt's just that I won't be going with everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.5733065407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、沙季と一緒に行くんだな！\n相変わらず二人は仲がいいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ so you're going with Saki!\nYou two are really close.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.9666760127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、相手はお姉ちゃんじゃないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I'm not going with my sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.9447126389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "なら……地元の友達か？\n東京にいたらなかなか会えないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then… a local friend?\nIt's hard to see them while in Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.3666760127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、相手はお友達じゃないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's not a friend either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.2196332177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "沙季でも友達でもないとなると……\nま、まさか相手は……男性じゃない、よな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's not Saki or a friend…\nIt can't be a… guy‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.4333426793,
      "sfxList": [
