          "startTime": 262.4633326817
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs028.m4a",
      "text": "え？　まぁ、男の人ではありますけど……\nあ、ちょっと失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Well‚ it is a guy‚ but…\nOh‚ excuse me for a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.0766399782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（男の人だと！？　千紗にそんな相手がいたなんて……）\n（ここは俺がアイドルの心得をしっかり教えないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（A guy!? I can't believe Chisa has someone like that…）\n（I need to make sure she understands her responsibilities as an idol.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.8000154495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs029.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、分かりました。よろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ I understand. Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 272.6354587516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs030.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、{user}さん\nさとみさんに呼ばれたので、私はこれで失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ {user}-san.\nSatomi-san called for me‚ so I have to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.8021396598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "……千紗。これだけは覚えておいてくれ\n俺は何があっても千紗の味方だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Chisa. Just remember this.\nI'll always be on your side no matter what.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.0333670933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "だから、事務所としての方針を整理して\n一度しっかり話をさせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ let's arrange a time to discuss\nthe agency's policies properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 293.1000317255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
